(15, 1, '2014-04-07 10:52:58', '2014-04-07 10:52:58', 'Please send any enquiries to <a href="mailto:info@acornequity.com">info@acornequity.com</a>\r\n\r\nAcorn Private Equity\r\nUnit A3 The Beach Head\r\n10 Niblick Way\r\nSomerset West\r\n7130\r\nSouth Africa\r\n\r\nTel: +27 (0)21 852 2887\r\nFax: +27 (0)21 852 3161\r\n\r\n<iframe style="line-height: 1.5em; border: 0px;" src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d211710.26768404906!2d18.618547500000002!3d-33.99322899999999!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x1dcdb559bdb4d867%3A0x3e5dcadd02c8f5a6!2s10+Niblick+Way!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1397139887019" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0"></iframe>\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2>Online Enquiry Form</h2>\r\n\r\n[contact-form-7 id="183" title="Contact form 1"]', 'Contact', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'contact', '', '', '2014-05-06 13:46:18', '2014-05-06 11:46:18', '', 0, 'http://localhost/~tyronestafford/acorn/?page_id=15', 0, 'page', '', 0),
