(271, 1, '2014-05-09 11:02:53', '2014-05-09 09:02:53', 'At the core of the Acorn Equity investment ethos is a commitment to delivering returns to our investors and contributing to the generation of long-term sustainable value for other stakeholders through the adoption of responsible investment practises focused on environmental, social and governance issues. Integral to the investment decision-making and portfolio management processes, and to the best of their ability, the Acorn Equity team is specifically committed to:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>Human rights</strong>\r\nRespect the protection of international human rights and avoid complicity in human rights violations.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Labour development and rights</strong>\r\nPromote sound labour development and rights practices, including considering employee working conditions, supporting the abolishment of child labour, promoting employees’ right to collective bargaining, eliminating forced labour, avoidance of employment discrimination and compliance with applicable labour laws.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>The environment</strong>\r\nTake a cautious and responsible approach to the environment, aiming to promote an appropriate level of environmental awareness and sound environmental practices in portfolio companies, including compliance with current environmental laws.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Anti-corruption</strong>\r\nAvoidance of corruption in all its forms and to subscribe to ethical behaviour that is captured in our membership to Unashamedly Ethical.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Robust corporate governance</strong>\r\nSeek to use governance structures that provide appropriate levels of oversight in the areas of audit, risk management and potential conflicts of interest, and to implement compensation and other policies that align the interests of owners and management.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nAcorn Private Equity will provide timely information and maintain an open and transparent dialogue with investors on the matters addressed herein.', 'Environmental, Social & Governance', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '82-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-05-09 11:02:53', '2014-05-09 09:02:53', '', 82, 'http://192.168.1.11/ACORN/website/htdocs/news/82-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(272, 1, '2014-05-09 12:19:43', '2014-05-09 10:19:43', '', 'About Acorn', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', 'about-acorn-2', '', '', '2014-05-09 12:19:43', '2014-05-09 10:19:43', '', 0, 'http://192.168.1.11/ACORN/website/htdocs/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/About-Acorn.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(287, 1, '2014-05-14 16:34:11', '2014-05-14 14:34:11', 'Acorn incorporated an investment holding company called Acorn Agri (Pty) Ltd in February 2014. Acorn Private Equity has a long-term management agreement in place with Acorn Agri (Pty) Ltd and is also a significant shareholder in the company.\r\n\r\nThe purpose of this investment company is to participate in the consolidation and growth in the Southern African agri sector. This will be achieved by acquiring significant stakes in strategic agri and food businesses to create a diversified portfolio by geography, commodity and type. By acquiring best of breed businesses in critical sectors, the investment company will create pockets of excellence ensuring regional food security and sustainable returns.\r\n\r\nAcorn Agri (Pty) Ltd has already raised R300 million from both individual and institutional investors for investment purposes.\r\n\r\nIn February 2014, Acorn Agri (Pty) Ltd acquired a 23% stake in Overberg Agri (Pty) Ltd, a diversified regional agri business, for R200 million. Further acquisitions are planned for the near future, with some negotiations at an advanced stage.\r\n\r\nAcorn Agri (Pty) Ltd is looking to raise further capital for future investments. Interested investors are welcome to contact us.\r\n\r\nFor more information, please visit the <a href="http://staging.fishgate.co.za/acorn_agri/" target="_blank">Acorn Agri website</a>.', 'Investment Company', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '72-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-05-14 16:34:11', '2014-05-14 14:34:11', '', 72, 'http://192.168.1.11/ACORN/website/htdocs/news/72-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(288, 1, '2014-05-26 12:57:39', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 'Auto Draft', '', 'auto-draft', 'open', 'open', '', '', '', '', '2014-05-26 12:57:39', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 0, 'http://192.168.1.11/ACORN/website/htdocs/?p=288', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(289, 1, '2014-05-27 10:59:31', '2014-05-27 08:59:31', '<strong>Acorn is a specialist private equity fund manager and investment advisor focused exclusively on Sub-Saharan Africa.</strong>\r\n\r\nFounded in 2009, Acorn is a dedicated partner to all our investee companies, fostering sustainable businesses and generating long-term value for all stakeholders.\r\n\r\nThe Acorn investment team is committed to exceptional performance, uncompromising integrity, honesty and ethical business practices. These principles allow us to encourage value creation and support growth as opposed to maximising returns to the detriment of our underlying portfolio companies.\r\n\r\nAcorn specialises in a vital but often-overlooked sector of the market, being small and medium enterprises. SMEs are a critical growth driver in Sub-Saharan Africa and capital invested in these enterprises truly has the power to transform those businesses and uplift communities. Well-managed investments in this sector can also earn an astute investor exceptional returns.', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '23-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-05-27 10:59:31', '2014-05-27 08:59:31', '', 23, 'http://192.168.1.11/ACORN/website/htdocs/news/23-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(290, 1, '2014-05-27 11:04:20', '2014-05-27 09:04:20', '<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Acorn is a specialist private equity fund manager and investment advisor focused exclusively on Sub-Saharan Africa.</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Founded in 2009, Acorn is a dedicated partner to all our investee companies, fostering sustainable businesses and generating long-term value for all stakeholders.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The Acorn investment team is committed to exceptional performance, uncompromising integrity, honesty and ethical business practices. These principles allow us to encourage value creation and support growth as opposed to maximising returns to the detriment of our underlying portfolio companies.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Acorn specialises in a vital but often-overlooked sector of the market, being small and medium enterprises. SMEs are a critical growth driver in Sub-Saharan Africa and capital invested in these enterprises truly has the power to transform those businesses and uplift communities. Well-managed investments in this sector can also earn an astute investor exceptional returns.</p>', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '23-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-05-27 11:04:20', '2014-05-27 09:04:20', '', 23, 'http://192.168.1.11/ACORN/website/htdocs/news/23-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(291, 1, '2014-05-27 11:11:34', '2014-05-27 09:11:34', '<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>Acorn is a specialist private equity fund manager and investment advisor focused exclusively on Sub-Saharan Africa.</strong></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Founded in 2009, Acorn is a dedicated partner to all our investee companies, fostering sustainable businesses and generating long-term value for all stakeholders.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">The Acorn investment team is committed to exceptional performance, uncompromising integrity, honesty and ethical business practices. These principles allow us to encourage value creation and support growth as opposed to maximising returns to the detriment of our underlying portfolio companies.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">Acorn specialises in a vital but often-overlooked sector of the market, being small and medium enterprises. SMEs are a critical growth driver in Sub-Saharan Africa and capital invested in these enterprises truly has the power to transform those businesses and uplift communities. Well-managed investments in this sector can also earn an astute investor exceptional returns.</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><a class="btn" title="The Firm" href="http://192.168.1.11/ACORN/website/htdocs/the-firm/">Read More</a></p>', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '23-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-05-27 11:11:34', '2014-05-27 09:11:34', '', 23, 'http://192.168.1.11/ACORN/website/htdocs/news/23-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(292, 1, '2014-05-27 11:21:20', '2014-05-27 09:21:20', 'To be respected members of the community and trusted custodians of capital, inspiring the confidence and loyalty of our investors by generating superior investment returns through responsible investing in a sustainable manner in close partnership with our investee companies.', 'OUR MISSION', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'our-mission', '', '', '2014-05-27 11:36:23', '2014-05-27 09:36:23', '', 0, 'http://192.168.1.11/ACORN/website/htdocs/?page_id=292', 0, 'page', '', 0),
